snippet.title: Bored Box X Evaverse Event
snippet.description:
We just celebrated the BoredBoard drops with an all day, in-game event! Thank you so much Bored Box for hosting an AMA/gaming session with our newest Evaverse players.

Nobody Walks in the Metaverse.
